# Using Forced Subtitles
# Many movies have subtitles encoded for secondary languages spoken during the film – when these are added to the movie, they are known as forced subtitles and are always visible (despite not being hard encoded). 
# Kodi (since v13 Gotham) recognizes and respects the forced flag for showing subtitles (even if subtitles are turned off by default, the forced flag will trigger them being turned on). 
*** This requires that the user have set the default languages in Settings in order to function properly. ***
# If there are multiple forced subtitles, Kodi will select the forced subtitles that match the default playback language.
